===Etymology===
[[File:Earthworm 01.jpg|thumb|[[earthworm|Earthworms]], such as this ''[[Lumbricus terrestris]]'', are '''detritivores''']]

From {{der|en|de|Detritivore}}, from {{der|en|la|dētrītus||the act of [[rub#Verb|rubbing]] away}} (from {{m|la|dēterō||to rub away, to [[rub off]], to [[wear out]]}}, from {{m|la|dē-||[[away#Preposition|away]]; [[down#Preposition|down]]}} + {{m|la|terō||to rub; to [[wear away]], to wear out}}, from {{der|en|ine-pro|*terh₁-||to rub, to rub by [[twist#Verb|twisting]]; to twist, to [[turn#Verb|turn]]}}) + {{der|en|la|vorāre}} (from {{m|la|vorō||to [[devour]], to [[eat]] [[greedily]]; to [[swallow#Verb|swallow]] up}}, from {{der|en|ine-pro|*gʷerh₃-||to devour}}).

